data.description: 3 bedroom, 1 bath, rock home on approximately 2 acres +/- ,just minutes from De Queen.  The home is approximately 1000 sq ft with CH&A, plus built on laundry room and porch.  Washer and dryer will stay.  Remodeled kitchen includes granite countertops and nice cabinets. Ceramic tile and laminate flooring.  Cute bathroom remodel and insulated windows.
